{
  "stem": "4760.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The was in June of 1939--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'38, '38.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'38.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister and I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just my sister and I went to France to our grandparents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our parents had to stay in-- in Germany because their paper-- their paperwork was not done in France to-- to immigrate into France.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were children so my grandparent covered-- covered that up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in 19-- in November of 1938, finally our parents arrived to France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the Kristallnacht, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything was broken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, there was not much left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they came to France.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the meantime, at the age of 14, I started to get a job, already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In-- in Europe, you know, you-- you can become an apprentice as soon you finish school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I became a baker, an apprentice baker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I worked in a bakery shop in the same town where my grandparents lived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And started working at the age of 14.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then my parents came in November of '38.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my grandparents got them an apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father would work for my grandparents, do some kind of chores, as-- as much as he could, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- in 19-- then in 1939, when the war broke out with Poland, my parents already got the notice because they were German, that they should not stay in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They should flee, go someplace in hiding, someplace not really hiding but not stay so close to the borderline.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So my parents moved to Limoges.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Limoges is in the Haute-Vienne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the southern part of France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in 1939, when the war broke out, my-- my boss was called to the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
